Norman Kerry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Norman_Kerry 0 Norman Kerry (born Norman Kaiser, June 16, 1894 – January 12, 1956) was an American actor whose career spanned over twenty-five years in the motion picture industry beginning in the silent era at the end of World War I.
